	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The homebrew scene has taken a long time to get to this point, a lot of trial and error and accumulated knowledge over the years.  It seems a waste to take all of that to make something as simple as a puzzle game that is also vaguely offensive and demeaning in premise.
<br />
<br />Of course this is most likely the intended response anyway, it's supposed to be deconstructionist/postmodern/whatever.  That doesn't mean much to me though.  I'll probably stick to <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ewAnUsGO-r4" class="postlink">my favorite concentration game</a> instead.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


